<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/main.css">
    <!-- Bootstrap core CSS -->
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-1BmE4kWBq78iYhFldvKuhfTAU6auU8tT94WrHftjDbrCEXSU1oBoqyl2QvZ6jIW3" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <!-- JavaScript Bundle with Popper -->
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-ka7Sk0Gln4gmtz2MlQnikT1wXgYsOg+OMhuP+IlRH9sENBO0LRn5q+8nbTov4+1p" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <title>충전페이지</title>
</head>
<body>
    <ul class="nav nav-pills nav-fill fixed-top navbar-light bg-light">
        <li class="nav-item py-2 px-1">
            <a class="nav-link active p-3" aria-current="page" href="/">메인</a>
        </li>
        <li class="nav-item py-2 px-1">
            <a class="nav-link active p-3" href="betting">베팅</a>    
        </li>
        <li class="nav-item py-2 px-1">
            <a class="nav-link active p-3" href="profile">내정보</a>
        </li>
        <li class="nav-item py-2 px-1">
            <a class="nav-link active p-3" href="/profile/charge">충전내역</a>
        </li>
    </ul>

    <!-- 결제페이지 경기정보 -->
    <form action="/charge/apply" method="post">
        <div class="container-fluid">
            <div class="card p-2 m-2" style="border: 2px solid black;">
                <div class="mb-3"><span>방식: </span><span>무통장입금</span></div>
                <div class="mb-5"><span>입금계좌: </span><span>938002-00-032087 국민은행 박수용</span></div>
                <div class="mb-5 text-center">입금하신 후 충전신청을 하면 1시간이내에 충전이 완료됩니다!</div>
                <div class="mb-3 text-center">충전금액의 10%에 해당하는 포인트를 추가로 드립니다</div>
                <div class="d-flex justify-content-center">
                    <span class="m-3">충전금액: </span>
                    <select class="form-select" name="money" onchange="updatePoint(this.value)" style="max-width:200px;" required>
                        <option value="" selected>금액선택</option>
                        <option value="5000">5천원</option>
                        <option value="10000">1만원</option>
                        <option value="30000">3만원</option>
                        <option value="50000">5만원</option>
                        <option value="100000">10만원</option>
                        <option value="500000">50만원</option>
                        <option value="1000000">100만원</option>
                    </select>
                </div>
                <div class="d-flex justify-content-center">
                    <span class="m-3">충전포인트: </span>
                    <input class="my-3 text-end" type="text" name="point" id="point" style="border:0; max-width: 200px;" readonly>
                    <span class="m-3 text-left">p</span>
                </div>
                <button type="submit" class="mt-3 btn btn-primary">충전신청</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </form>
    <script src="/js/charge_change_point.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
